	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As I have no skills in designing hardware-mappers, I'm just curious if these ideas were possible with the PowerPak:
<br />
<br />* Being able to map PRGROM at $6000?
<br />* Instead of mirroring, map "real" memory at $800-&gt; (where the main RAM is mirrored in normal case). 
<br />* Being able to swap between CHRRAM and CHRROM in the same mapper?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


